import '../styles/TraineeCard.css' import {Link} from 'react-router-dom' import {useState, useEffect} from 'react' import AcademyCardList from './AcademyCardList' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import axios from 'axios' const TraineeCard = (props) => { const navigate = useNavigate() const {id, name, stream, academy} = props.trainee var trainee_id = props.trainee_id const handleSubmit = () => { navigate('/ListExams/' + trainee_id ) } return(

{name}

Stream: {stream.name}
Academy: {academy.name}
) } export default TraineeCard
